display_content.json_block:
{"language": "html", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ESCON: 개념적 보완 제안 | McKinsey Style</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Source+Serif+4:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');

  :root {
    --mckinsey-blue: #003366;
    --mckinsey-navy: #001a33;
    --accent: #0066CC;
    --accent-light: #4d9de0;
    --gold: #C8A84B;
    --warm-gray: #F5F3EF;
    --mid-gray: #8A8A8A;
    --dark-gray: #333333;
    --border: #D4D0C8;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --red-accent: #C0392B;
    --green-accent: #1A7A4A;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
    background: #E8E4DC;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  /* SLIDE CONTAINER */
  .deck {
    max-width: 1060px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .slide {
    background: var(--white);
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  /* TOP RULE */
  .slide::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    width: 100%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* SLIDE INNER */
  .slide-inner {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 32px 48px 24px;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* SLIDE NUMBER */
  .slide-number {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 20px;
    right: 48px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  /* LOGO AREA */
  .slide-logo {
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 48px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ─── COVER SLIDE ─── */
  .slide-cover {
    background: var(--mckinsey-navy);
  }
  .slide-cover::before { background: var(--gold); }

  .cover-inner {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px 64px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cover-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cover-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 46px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .cover-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .cover-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: auto;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }

  .cover-meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .cover-meta-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .cover-meta-value {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* Decorative element on cover */
  .cover-deco {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 280px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(200,168,75,0.08) 0%, rgba(0,102,204,0.12) 100%);
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(200,168,75,0.15);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 40px;
  }

  .cover-deco-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 72px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(200,168,75,0.25);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .cover-deco-text {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: rgba(200,168,75,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* ─── SECTION HEADER ─── */
  .section-header {
    background: var(--warm-gray);
  }

  .sh-inner {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 64px;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .sh-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 80px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(0,51,102,0.1);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 100px;
  }

  .sh-content {}

  .sh-overline {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .sh-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 34px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .sh-body {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  /* ─── CONTENT SLIDE ─── */
  .slide-head {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .slide-headline {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    line-height: 1.2;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--mckinsey-blue);
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .slide-subhead {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  /* TWO COLUMN LAYOUT */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .three-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .col-box {
    background: var(--warm-gray);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 18px 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .col-box-accent {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
  }

  .col-box.gold .col-box-accent { background: var(--gold); }
  .col-box.red .col-box-accent { background: var(--red-accent); }
  .col-box.green .col-box-accent { background: var(--green-accent); }
  .col-box.light-blue .col-box-accent { background: var(--accent-light); }

  .box-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .box-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .box-body {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    line-height: 1.55;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* INSIGHT BAR */
  .insight-bar {
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .insight-bar-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .insight-bar-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* FRAMEWORK DIAGRAM */
  .framework {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .fw-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 160px 40px 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .fw-left {
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .fw-left-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .fw-left-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .fw-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0,51,102,0.08);
    color: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .fw-right {
    background: var(--warm-gray);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .fw-right-current {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--red-accent);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .fw-right-needed {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--green-accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* MATRIX */
  .matrix-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr 1fr;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .matrix-cell {
    background: var(--white);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .matrix-header {
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .matrix-row-header {
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    writing-mode: horizontal-tb;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 12px 8px;
  }

  .matrix-corner { background: var(--mckinsey-navy); }

  .matrix-content {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    text-align: left;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .matrix-content.highlight { background: rgba(0,51,102,0.06); }

  .matrix-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .matrix-text {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* ROADMAP */
  .roadmap {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .roadmap::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 60px;
    right: 60px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
    z-index: 0;
    transform: translateY(-20px);
  }

  .roadmap-item {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .roadmap-dot {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 3px solid var(--white);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--mckinsey-blue);
  }

  .roadmap-dot.gold {
    background: var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--gold);
  }

  .roadmap-dot.light {
    background: var(--accent-light);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--accent-light);
  }

  .roadmap-content {
    background: var(--warm-gray);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .roadmap-phase {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .roadmap-title {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .roadmap-text {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* CONCLUSION */
  .slide-conclusion {
    background: var(--mckinsey-navy);
  }

  .slide-conclusion::before { background: var(--gold); }

  .conclusion-inner {
    flex: 1;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .conclusion-left {
    padding: 32px 48px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .conclusion-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .conclusion-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .conclusion-body {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .conclusion-right {
    background: rgba(200,168,75,0.08);
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(200,168,75,0.2);
    padding: 32px 36px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .conclusion-point {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .conclusion-point-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 24px;
  }

  .conclusion-point-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding-top: 4px;
  }

  /* QUOTE SLIDE */
  .quote-inner {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 32px 80px;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .big-quote-mark {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 80px;
    color: rgba(0,51,102,0.12);
    line-height: 0.6;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .big-quote-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 24px;
    color: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .big-quote-text em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
  }

  .big-quote-source {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* DIVIDER LINE */
  .h-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 12px 0;
  }

  /* TAG PILL */
  .pill {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .pill.gold { background: var(--gold); }
  .pill.light { background: var(--accent-light); }

  /* STAT */
  .stat-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--mckinsey-blue);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* TOP LABEL BAR */
  .top-label-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .top-label-main {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .top-label-sep {
    width: 1px;
    height: 12px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .top-label-sub {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--mid-gray);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  /* PRINT */
  @media print {
    body { background: white; padding: 0; }
    .deck { gap: 0; }
    .slide { page-break-after: always; aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="deck">

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 1: COVER
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="slide slide-cover">
    <div style="height:6px; background:var(--gold); flex-shrink:0;"></div>
    <div class="cover-inner">
      <div class="cover-label">ESCON Framework Review · 2025</div>
      <div class="cover-title">엔지니어는 왜<br>이 툴을 자신의<br>문제로 보지 않는가</div>
      <div class="cover-subtitle">개념적 전환을 통한 ESCON 임팩트 강화 전략 — 6가지 핵심 보완 프레임</div>
      <div class="cover-meta">
        <div class="cover-meta-item">
          <span class="cover-meta-label">대상</span>
          <span class="cover-meta-value">실무 엔지니어 수용성 제고</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cover-meta-item">
          <span class="cover-meta-label">시스템</span>
          <span class="cover-meta-value">ESCON — ESCO 기반 스킬 온톨로지</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cover-meta-item">
          <span class="cover-meta-label">핵심 명제</span>
          <span class="cover-meta-value">지도는 완성됐다. 이제 내 위치를 찍어야 한다.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="cover-deco">
      <div class="cover-deco-num">6</div>
      <div class="cover-deco-text">개념적<br>보완 영역</div>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-number">01</div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       SLIDE 2: SITUATION — 핵심 문제 진단
  ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-inner">
      <div class="slide-logo">ESCON · Situation</div>
      <div class="slide-headline">문제 진단: ESCON은 훌륭한 지도이나, 엔지니어는 자신의 위치를 찾을 수 없다</div>
      <div class="slide-subhead">현재 상태(As-Is)와 필요 상태(To-Be)의 개념적 간극</div>

      <div class="two-col" style="gap:20px; flex:1;">
        <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:10px;">
          <div class="col-box red">
            <div class="col-box-accent"></div>
            <div class="box-label">AS-IS · 현재 설계 철학</div>
            <div class="box-title">조직 관리자의 시선으로 구성된 탐색 시스템</div>
            <div class="box-body">ESCON은 도메인 탐색, 스킬 네트워크, 유사도 비교 기능을 제공하나, 진입점은 HR 기획자의 분석 언어로 구성되어 있다. 엔지니어가 자연스럽게 자신의 문제와 연결하기 어려운 구조.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-box green">
